<br />Then the only real answer is that it cannot be justified to people who believe this.
<br />
<br />Doing an activity that "won't sell" does not equate to something that has no value.  There are possibly more worthy pursuits, but there will always be more worthy pursuits than whatever you are currently doing.  You could also be doing a lot worse.</div>

